    <item>
      <title>海军部长约翰·费兰即将离开五角大楼和特朗普政府</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/navy-secretary-john-phelan.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与皮特·赫格斯和其他五角大楼领导人关系紧张数月后，约翰·费兰即将离开五角大楼。这场骚乱发生之际，美国海军正与伊朗交战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/navy-secretary-john-phelan.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 01:34:48 GMT</pubDate>
